  "original_title": "\u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf \u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bcb\u0baa\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb4\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "COPE Committee invites Litro to investigate gas distribution infrastructure",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Committee on Government Accountability Initiatives (COP), the Committee on Government Accounts (COPA) and the Committee on Government Finance will meet this week. Litro Company and Litro Terminal Lanka Company have come forward to COPE Group to investigate the gas distribution structure.",
        "The Ministry of Transport and Highways will appear before the Gopa Committee headed by Prof. Tissa Vidharana on Tuesday 05th to examine the current critical situation of the Public Transport Department and the next step.",
        "Also, the Ministerial Advisory Committee on Urban Development and Housing will meet on 05th under the chairmanship of Minister Prasanna Ranatunga.",
        "Also, the committee chaired by Anura Priyadarshana Yappa, Committee on Government Accounts, will meet on 05th and the Inland Revenue Department has been invited to the committee.",
        "Meanwhile, Sri Lanka Public Utilities Commission will be invited to the COP meeting on Wednesday 06th."
      ],
